<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我找彩蛋的时候<delay20 />一不小心太投入了，<delay8 />
感觉明天会肌肉酸痛，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以现在正待在家里休息呢！
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你也要记得适当休息一下哦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />今天<delay8 />
来广场上了呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然他给人一种难以形容的印象，<delay20 />
但他为了庆祝复活节，<delay8 />可是事先做足了<delay8 />
各式各样的准备，<delay20 /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人超级好的对吧～？
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我们也得好好享受才行！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻，<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />复活节快乐！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我想把面包和点心制作得可爱一点，<delay20 />
这样可以烘托出复活节的气氛～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把面团弄成兔子的形状，<delay8 />
用各色糖果加以点缀～<delay20 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再放点洋芹怎么样？！
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />烤好之后
也分给你一些吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<10_4 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦，<delay20 />你不要？<delay40 /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为什么呀～？</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">对了，<delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />偷偷告诉你一件事～<delay20 />
是我从陆德里那听说的！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />关于会掉出彩蛋的岩石的<delay8 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />小<delay8 />秘<delay8 />密！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前用里数旅行券参加旅行的人，<delay20 />
在旅途目的地不小心被岩石绊到了脚，<delay40 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那个岩石里面<delay20 /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然一下子
掉出来了<delay8 />彩蛋！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听到这么奇妙的事情，<delay20 />
不觉得特别令人兴奋吗？<delay40 />
你要是感兴趣，就去确认一下吧！<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总觉得<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="33" />的所有人<delay20 />
都在满心期待复活节的到来！<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻，<delay20 />应该不是只有我这样吧？
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有听过关于奇妙椰子树的传闻吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也只是道听途说的就是啦。
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />据说只要从侧面敲击椰子树，<delay20 />
就会有很多彩蛋掉出来哦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这到底是为什么呀？！
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道<delay20 />彩蛋其实是椰子的后代吗？！<delay40 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />开玩笑的啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你如果<delay20 />感兴趣，就去确认一下吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
听说今年的复活节<delay20 />是<tag a="90" b="35" arg="0xcd00" />月<tag a="90" b="36" arg="0xcd00" />日哦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这可是我特别喜欢的活动～！
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />色彩柔和～<delay20 />潮流时尚～<delay20 />
那种可爱的氛围<delay8 />
真是太棒啦～！
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那些装饰得精巧可爱的彩蛋，<delay8 />
简直就是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可爱元素的集合体呀～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>